500
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:11,527
Hindi kita sinisisi.

501
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:14,960
Hindi ko naman inaasahan na kikita nang malaki ang Xuan Island .

502
00:28:14,960 --> 00:28:16,680
Akala ko hindi pa rin ito kumikita.

503
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:18,000
